dct_title_s: Delaware and Raritan Canal historic map
dct_description_sm: This is a historic map outlining the course of the Delaware and Raritan canal through New Jersey. It also contains a short history of its construction from the early 1800s.
Based on the 1866 Geologic map which shows the towns, streets, roads, railroads, canals and drainage at that time.
